1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,800
Día uno...

2
00:00:00,800 --> 00:00:01,880
pedaleando
por Valencia

3
00:00:01,880 --> 00:00:02,880
después del curro.

4
00:00:02,880 --> 00:00:03,840
A ver qué pasa.

5
00:00:03,840 --> 00:00:04,640
Me subo
a la bici,

6
00:00:04,640 --> 00:00:05,520
sin plan.

7
00:00:05,520 --> 00:00:06,320
Las calles,
el aire,

8
00:00:06,320 --> 00:00:07,200
el barrio.

9
00:00:07,200 --> 00:00:08,400
Para mí esto es
desconectar

10
00:00:08,400 --> 00:00:09,240
de verdad.

11
00:00:09,240 --> 00:00:09,840
Y lo que mola

12
00:00:09,840 --> 00:00:11,120
es que a veces
encuentras cosas

13
00:00:11,120 --> 00:00:11,720
que aún sirven

14
00:00:11,720 --> 00:00:12,520
y las compartes.

15
00:00:12,520 --> 00:00:13,720
Que alguien
las use.

16
00:00:13,720 --> 00:00:15,080
Hay gente
haciendo esto

17
00:00:15,080 --> 00:00:15,680
cada día.

18
00:00:15,680 --> 00:00:16,360
En bici,
andando,

19
00:00:16,360 --> 00:00:17,360
da igual cómo.

20
00:00:17,360 --> 00:00:17,880
Guardad esto

21
00:00:17,880 --> 00:00:18,760
para cuando
necesitéis

22
00:00:18,760 --> 00:00:19,840
desconectar.

23
00:00:19,840 --> 00:00:20,720
Funciona.

